Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.28,0:00:08.40,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:09.70,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:11.32,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yu-Yumeko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:13.26,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What might you be looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:15.49,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Ah, no... this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:18.76,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This girl's a really popular indie-idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.76,0:00:21.18,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,and at the same time a member of the Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:24.54,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,My. Someone like that was in the Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.54,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumemite Yumemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:29.08,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,She’s a second year student and publicity manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:32.10,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Some of her YourTube videos \Nget over three million views.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:35.76,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,People say she's guaranteed to be a big \Nhit if she ever makes a major debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:39.08,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,She sometimes holds concerts on school grounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:42.85,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,but she's so popular that you have to be in her fan club to get tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:45.56,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You certainly are well-informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:51.82,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I’d like to cheer her on, as a fellow schoolmate, \Nbut the entrance fees are just too high...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.60,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:55.97,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If you liked it, then I’m counting \Non you to spread the love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:00:58.97,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Share me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:01.83,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:03.45,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.80,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:49.81,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:52.69,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Just where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:55.07,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You never even told me where you were going...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.59,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving the academy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:59.40,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I have to take care of some minor business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.75,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What could it possibly be at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:04.61,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Just yesterday, Ikishima-san \Nlost to Jabami Yumeko–
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:05.40,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:07.81,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That's why I have business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:13.79,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Deal with the leftovers as you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:14.82,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.67,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.75,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If you're not present, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:20.22,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.25,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Like a broken record...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:30.58,Kakegurui - Italic,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A week has passed since then. {\i0}{Italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:33.42,Kakegurui - Italic,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Student Council is by no means a monolith. {\i0}{Italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.42,Kakegurui - Italic,,0,0,0,,Those that seek out power...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:37.46,Kakegurui - Italic,,0,0,0,,Those who want to protect themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:39.51,Kakegurui - Italic,,0,0,0,,Those who pursue pleasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:41.72,Kakegurui - Italic,,0,0,0,,And those that cannot be read.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:46.87,Kakegurui - Italic,,0,0,0,,What connects us all are the foundations built upon \Nthe absolute authority of the Council President…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.74,Kakegurui - Italic,,0,0,0,,The influence we possess as \Na Student Council members.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:54.65,Kakegurui - Italic,,0,0,0,,But with the appearance of Jabami Yumeko, \Nour state of affairs is beginning to waver...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:58.07,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's been a week since Ikishima's shameful display.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.59,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The Council President isn't attending school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:05.80,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That is... I was not told the \Nreasoning behind it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:11.06,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,And here I thought \Nshe’d let you know, of all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.33,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Nyahahahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.69,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Then we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.08,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We may be on our own,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:19.07,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,but why don't we decide how to deal with the two that lost against the livestock?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:23.53,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Neither Ikishima-san nor \Nnishinotouin-san have lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:27.69,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That's only because of the President’s \Naid and their opponent’s pity, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:31.03,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Rumours are already spreading \Nthroughout school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:33.10,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The Student Council's dignity is taking a fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:35.34,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,How disappointing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:37.79,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,How can you go on as a member, \Npretending nothing happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.15,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Manyuda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:41.52,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You’re showing great \Ndisrespect towards a Third Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:47.22,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The concept of disrespect \Ndoesn’t exist in this academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:53.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You should know better, considering that you’re \Nalways at the President’s side, Igarashi Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.67,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Then why don’t you try and take on Yumeko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:03.03,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,And why exactly should \NI waste my time on mere livestock?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:05.11,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumeko, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.09,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,She got guts and insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:08.73,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,She trusts her allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:11.60,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,She has everything she needs for success.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.63,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,And more than anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.68,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Those eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.44,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Just remembering them is enough for me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:24.17,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Ikishima-san, the meeting is still underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.79,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\pos(608.962,762)}Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:29.79,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\pos(710.512,762)}room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:29.79,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\pos(850.491,762)}break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:34.06,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I really can't stand that eccentric side of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:38.81,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I don't think Ikishima-san's \Ncomments are that far off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Jabami Yumeko is livestock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.90,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That is exactly what makes her so terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:47.28,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If she uses her privilege as livestock to \Nchallenge the President to an official match...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:50.28,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Depending on the outcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.28,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The President becomes livestock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.79,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If you lose you're treated like \Neveryone else, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:58.04,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I will never let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.47,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I oppose that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:04.67,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,More importantly, what about collecting our debts to weaken her funds?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:06.82,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:09.17,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That’s been forbidden by the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:12.08,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Not to mention she's already assigned a Life Plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.31,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yep. I guess she passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:17.73,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You just leave Yumeko-chan to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:19.82,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumemite, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.23,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumemite-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.23,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I’m gonna take on Yumeko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.77,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:31.07,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You are indeed someone easily capable of creating stage to utterly crush Jabami Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.35,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:36.34,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,And since it’s such a rare opportunity, \NI wanna go all flashy about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:38.83,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Manyuda-kun, I'd like your help too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.26,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:43.19,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I’ll accept all responsibility of \Norganising this plan of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.17,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Please wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.42,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The President gave orders…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.18,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\i1}T-This is hopeless. {\i0}{Italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:52.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can hardly hold them back on my own. {\i0}{Italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:56.29,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On top of that, I cannot even begin to comprehend the nature of the President's will...{\i0}{Italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.95,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I’m telling you, it’ll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:02.02,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Just leave this to us Second Years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:06.44,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's about time for the Student Council to start \Nthinking about the next generation, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:16.43,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Did something good happen to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:18.08,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.91,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,She's been like that all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:23.67,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there \Nwas something in that letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.24,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:26.80,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Jabami-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:28.77,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:32.30,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,1st year Flower Class, \Nsumeragi Itsuki arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.54,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Surprise! {Jyaaaaan~}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:37.44,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,A Traditional Montblanc from \Nseifuudou. Dropping it off here! {Montblanc, yummy}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:39.23,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that our...? {our/for us?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:41.14,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,They're delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:43.23,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I know about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:46.67,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You were kicked out of the \Nstudent Council a few days ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:50.13,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,So, now you plan to suck up to Yumeko
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:53.36,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,to find some weakness that gives you a chance to get back into the Council, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:54.68,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,How shallow! {Angel Beats reference! Keep it in! Trust me guys... Guys?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:56.85,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:08:00.04,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'd do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:08.11,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.30,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I’ll spill the beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:13.09,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:17.07,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The president of one of Japan’s \Ntop toy makers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:20.19,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous you have a \Nbright future laid out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:23.10,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It’s... not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:26.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,My father’s pragmatic to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.25,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I was to enter this academy and join the Student Council,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:33.11,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,then establish connections to the elites of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:37.39,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If I can't do that... worst case, \NI might get disowned!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.86,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Jabami-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:42.10,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you’re aiming for the \Nposition of Student Council President?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:44.57,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's a rumour...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:49.57,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,A rumour that’s being perpetuated and talked \Nabout by students, especially the livestock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:54.74,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Even after winning at the Debt Adjustment Assembly you decided
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:56.72,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,to stay as livestock voluntarily....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:09:01.31,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,They’re saying it was all to retain the right \Nto challenge the President for her position!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:08.83,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yumeko just came here to \Ngamble in any way she liked. {\i0}{Italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:09.81,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But still… {\i0}{Italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:15.19,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before we even noticed, the whole \Nacademy started revolving around her! {\i0}{Italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:20.69,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If these rumours really are true, \Nthen there's only one thing for me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:24.73,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I want you to make me a member of the Student Council again
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.92,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,after you take the President's position!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:30.49,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,For that, there’s nothing I won’t do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:34.42,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This is how I really feel, \Nno lies involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:40.41,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I’m begging you. \Nplease make me an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.43,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I welcome you with \Nopen arms, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:45.89,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Setting aside the issue with the \Nstudent Council President...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.12,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We both really enjoy gambling, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:53.82,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That already makes us friends, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.23,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,T-That's true…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:01.44,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is she really that deluded? {\i0}{Italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:02.64,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That girl… {\i0}{Italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.93,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Dvds are over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.22,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The new song's Cds are available here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:12.65,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,As always, that was a superb concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.86,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Shinnouji-kun, you came today too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.21,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Of course I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:20.56,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,As the president of your fan club \NI can't afford to miss a single show!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:24.26,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the timing of our cheers \Nduring 'Gambling Girl' was a bit off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:26.16,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure it'll be better next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:28.78,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,All in moderation, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:29.83,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:32.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,As a fan awaiting your major debut,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.79,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I have an obligation to lecture the others on proper conduct!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:36.09,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,As the president, \Nthat’s my responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:41.05,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I mean, those lazy bums are slacking \Non their 100 views per day quota!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:44.39,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying they should load the \Nvideo on five different phones like I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:47.06,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,but if they can't give you at least a hundred views
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.98,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,they shouldn't be allowed to be called a fan of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:07.18,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,All of those pigs are fucking disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:16.20,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Would you rather cancel the handshake event after your live performance, at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.23,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:24.24,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's not just the concert; it’s the personal \NInteractions that keep them coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:26.28,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:28.23,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Saori.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:31.18,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,For my dreams, this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:35.50,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If I can't handle this much, \NI'll never achieve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:40.20,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,More importantly, when \Nare we challenging Yumeko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.78,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,By tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:45.50,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We've already received the funds necessary thanks to Manyuda-san’s organisation skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:48.34,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I see. I'm looking forward to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:55.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'll make Yumeko-chan bet \Nher whole life on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:58.78,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Eh? A gamble with Yumemite-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:02.28,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Indeed. I just had the pleasure \Nto speak to her manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:04.25,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is serious... {\i0}{Italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:07.86,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yumeko's been taking down the \Nstudent Council members one by one. {\i0}{Italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:11.17,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no doubt about it... \Nyumeko's being targeted! {\i0}{Italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:14.63,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Okay then, Manyuda-kun. \Ntake care of the rest, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:15.91,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:19.17,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,With the Council President gone, \Nthis is the perfect chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:23.28,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We Second Years will have the total \Npower of the Council in our grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:26.40,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'll begin with the preparations for the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:29.88,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Make sure that Jabami doesn't \Npull the rug out from under you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:34.15,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Manyuda-kun, you're such a worrywart...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.41,0:12:41.34,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Would it be alright to take Suzui-san with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:43.61,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,A boy... you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.99,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Well, it should be fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.84,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:47.83,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:50.40,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:51.77,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'll get her permission now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:55.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I apologise. I just couldn't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:58.67,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Before you enter, \Nplease let me conduct a full-body search.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:00.07,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Every now and then,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:03.62,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,some people try to enter the waiting room with cameras and recording devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:05.53,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Of course. I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:12.08,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Come on in! I'm Yumemite Yumemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:14.04,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'm working as an idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.79,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you, Yumemite-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.98,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Oh? Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:22.80,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Um...! W-Well... I'm from the \Nsecond Year Flower Class, Suzui–
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:24.15,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Suzui Ryouta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:24.49,Kakegurui - Up,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.56,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You came to one of my live performances, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:30.04,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It was during last year's school festival! \Non the second day of my live performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:30.81,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:35.21,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I-I'm surprised you even remember that. \NIt was such a long time ago, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:40.23,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I remember the names and faces of all my fans! \Nas an idol, that's a given!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:43.53,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Now then, what kind of gamble \Ndo you have in mind for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:45.57,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Right, right. The gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.30,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:50.41,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,"Battle to determine the top-class idol"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:54.31,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It kind of sounds like some sort of variety program...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:57.25,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The plan's actually supposed to be for Tv,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:14:00.71,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,but I really wanted to \Ngo on stage with Yumeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.94,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,After my live performance, \Nright in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:06.49,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,As long as I won't be a bother, I don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.63,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,There's no way you'd bother me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:12.47,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Because, this gamble's supposed to double as a new member election!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:13.75,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.93,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The stakes'll be 50,000,000 Yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:19.25,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,With that much, you can get out of being livestock, right? {450,000 Usd}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:19.98,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:25.70,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,So! If I win, your debt's \Nobviously gonna get higher...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:26.94,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,So, when that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:30.03,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'm having you form an idol unit with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:30.78,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:35.93,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I had your Life Plan Forms written out that way! \Nthe unit's been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.36,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Its name, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:40.02,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Dreaming Creaming Sisters! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:43.24,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Wow. E-Embarra–
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:48.26,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Both of our names have the character for \N'dream'! This is fate, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:52.06,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,But still, an idol's life isn't all fun and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:55.75,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The lessons are strict, \Nand having no private lives is a given...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:58.83,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,And of course, \Nhaving a love life is out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:02.73,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumeko-chan, I'm having you \Nrisk it all on an idol life too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:04.27,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:07.44,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,But nevertheless, why would you \Ngo to such an extent as an idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:10.33,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,For the smiles of my fans, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:13.06,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Please leave that facade of yours aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:16.95,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumemite-san, you despise your fans, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:22.25,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What are you even saying? \Nthere's no way that's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.94,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:26.63,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Then just what might this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:33.90,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Let's read this, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:36.38,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,To Our Beloved Yumemi-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:40.69,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,As always, thank you for a fun \Nlive show! Also, good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:43.65,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Recently, you've gotten pretty popular on YourTube,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:46.20,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,and I'm truly proud \Nas the head of your fanclub.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.32,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Teehee~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:52.23,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,But as a long-time fan, \NI'm kind of lonely. (Lol).
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:54.91,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I've been really busy \Nwith studying lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:57.48,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,but whenever I see \Nyou doing your best–
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:15:58.62,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:00.26,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumemi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:02.58,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's exactly like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.40,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,But so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:08.33,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,To think that you would continue working as \Nan idol, despite your contempt for your fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:11.92,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You must have quite \Nthe lofty goals in mind, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:16.43,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Having never heard of them, \NI feel rather left out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:23.74,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I want an Academy Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:26.76,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I've been admiring it since I was little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:31.19,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The air that only allowed those blessed with talents,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:33.61,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,raw ability, and fortune to walk in its vicinity...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:37.83,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The entire world focuses on \Nevery little movement they make.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:42.21,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I want to become one of those \Nlone flowers that paint the red carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.71,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I signed up with a talent agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:50.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,went through lessons every day, and became a Tv regular faster than anyone else in my class!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:53.58,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,But then I realised... this was too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.47,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Even if things went well,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:59.34,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,there'd be no guarantee that 'd stand at the top of this small-minded country called Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:02.77,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If I wanted to obtain some epic role of importance at Hollywood,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:04.99,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,there was an entirely different approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:07.35,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That would be this academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:09.52,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,And being an idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:14.36,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,As long as I have this academy's support, \Ntaking the top as an idol isn't impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:17.20,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Once I reach the height of my popularity and move on to being an actress,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.74,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I can stand among Japan's top class!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:24.54,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}And if I make it that far, \NIt's not too hard to debut in a Hollywood film!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:27.38,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:31.65,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,For that, you would continue despite your hatred of interacting with your fans?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:32.67,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:36.81,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,In their case, I can't say that \NI care about how bad they look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:41.25,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That just means that they're spending \Nmore money on me than on themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:42.27,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:45.07,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Why the Hell do they dance like crazy during my live shows?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:47.28,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If you've got time to dance, then listen to my damn song!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:50.62,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Why are you working up more sweat than I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:54.96,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Accepting those sweat-soaked \Nhandshakes of yours is disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.24,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Being an idol is rather tough, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:04.33,Kakegurui - Up,,0,0,0,,You should start getting ready. \Nyou'll be doing the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:06.46,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Until I listened to that story of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:10.51,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I can't say that I ever thought of becoming an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:14.41,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,But the very idea of offering one's \Nentire life to such a profession...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:17.40,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That is quite the marvelous risk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:20.72,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to teach you thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:25.43,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, if we were to both risk our entire lives instead of relying on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:27.56,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,this gamble would be all the more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:28.48,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:31.94,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:38.17,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I've taken the liberty of \Nrecording our little conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:42.05,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,In all honesty, I thought that only \Nbringing a ripped letter wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:46.93,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Should this be released to the public, \Nyour life as an idol would surely meet an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:55.83,Kakegurui - Up,,0,0,0,,{\fs45}Why are you working up more sweat than I am?! Accepting those sweat-soaked handshakes of yours is disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:56.07,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumeko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.65,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\pos(403.499,761.625)}Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:58.65,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\pos(774,762)}Why does Saori have that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.30,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,No, this isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.01,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Back then... {Italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:07.22,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,For you, Yumemite-san, why don't \Nwe use this voice recorder for our bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:09.19,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Hand that over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:15.19,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Please, rest assured. I wouldn't do something as \Nunderhanded as to keep another copy on hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:18.90,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,As long as I can gamble, then I'm satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:24.96,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Well then, I do look forward \Nto the day of our gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:27.45,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Um... Well... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:30.92,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:37.22,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:41.54,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Because of me, your... our dreams are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:52.89,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This is fine, bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:58.11,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Jabami Yumeko. I swear to you, \NI'll make you regret underestimating me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:04.73,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumeko... That voice recorder...{}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:08.02,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I found it together with the torn fan letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:10.79,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,All I was told was, \N"Use this and threaten her".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:14.15,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I wonder, just whose \Nwork could it have been?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:15.29,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:20.22,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I thought I put that letter away here to burn it later...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:22.72,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We were paying close attention to the doors, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:27.09,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone could \Nsteal in front of me or you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:31.18,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That means that the culprit \Nhas to have a master key...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:34.46,Kakegurui - Up,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please leave a message after the tone. {\i0}{Italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:39.62,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello? Prez, you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:43.23,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Things are really \Nheating up 'round here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:49.73,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}If you don't come back soon, then don't blame \Nme for what's gonna happen to this school!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:02.09,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That was 'You're a Black Jack'!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.79,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Thank you, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:06.99,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You're the best! {pronounced font}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:11.06,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,As sad as it is, today's \Nlive performance ends here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:13.09,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)}Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:18.44,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,But just like we announced, we'll be starting \Nwith the New Member Election!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:21.94,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's finally Yumeko's turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:25.80,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Still, is it really that bad to \Nnot be here until she finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:29.82,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Like I said, you didn't have to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:33.83,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I just made preparations for as many people \Nas Jabami-senpai wanted me to, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:39.25,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Saotome, these tickets \Naren't exactly easy to come by.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:44.52,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Honestly. How hard do you think I had to work \Nto get the fanclub president to fork them over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:47.59,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I get it already. I already heard that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.65,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Alright then, let's introduce her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.65,0:21:51.59,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you all know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:56.05,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,She's been advancing ever since \Nshe transferred here last month...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:22:00.71,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,From Hyakkaou Academy's Second Year, \Nflower Class - it's Jabami Yumeko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:12.49,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,She really is adorable when you see \Nher like that, that Jabami-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:19.58,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumeko-chan. Go on, \Nshow your enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.20,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I've never had a chance like this, \Nso I do feel a tad nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:26.26,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,But I'll be sure to enjoy it to its fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:28.11,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:30.01,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,With that said, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:34.69,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,A battle that decides the top idol, \N"You May Battle"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.69,0:22:37.67,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Here it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.47,0:24:11.78,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumemi-chan, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.63,0:24:13.23,Kakegurui - Up,,0,0,0,,That... that's just a battle of luck, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.85,0:24:14.20,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's nothing more than luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.20,0:24:15.86,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Is that not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.33,0:24:16.51,Kakegurui - Up,,0,0,0,,Keep quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:21.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,And thank you all for cheering me on up until now...
